title: 7 AM Hour - Should Disney Have To Apologize For This?
description:
Happy Monday! Dave is LIVE from Boston a good chunk of this week but you can hardly tell! Falen is gearing up for her trip to Spain and we got a whole lot of laughs today!

Something went down at Disney and people are speculating if they should have to apologize, Think Fast: Dave vs Falen, Farts in a jar email, Monday Motivation, & More!
